{"tid":1030104,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果孫中山或者袁世凱當年立到憲 依家既中國會好似日本同泰國一樣咁美好 蔡鍔係近代中國大罪人","createTime":"2019-02-20T17:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T12:12:35.000Z","uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09a992cfec043aae31316f5ea97ded455d7e3853","tid":1030104,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:33:58.000Z","msg":"孫中山反清前期曾經諗過係稱帝架<br />\n但之後左膠上腦搞咩民國<br />\n最慘係袁世凱 都稱到帝架啦 本應可以帶中國走向立憲既道路<br />\n只可惜比個屎忽鬼蔡鍔玩撚死左<br />\n共產黨就係民國管唔掂咁大個中國先慢慢崛起 真係好唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反日泰仲有個名義上既君主喺度<br />\n成個國家都係琴瑟和諧<br />\n唔會咁多爭鬥 好舒服架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30286ec216670ba7eba5963d744e98f40ef91d2d","tid":1030104,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:35:39.000Z","msg":"算啦 歷史無如果架"},{"pid":"c6128567eabe6a2c74a2cacb8525ad2f08009243","tid":1030104,"uid":196050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"西安事變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060bae8617a973196197865e6fac25c699250240","tid":1030104,"uid":7057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"滿人君主立憲應該搞唔掂漢人<br />\n袁呢d冇幾代歷史backup更加唔洗提"},{"pid":"856176bab5ceec523247fd26f4e7ae5069b7c869","tid":1030104,"uid":164166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"你要玩如果 咁不如話晚清出咗君主立憲 冇搞咩皇室內閣 咪搞掂晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國國運過去呢一百年一直係向壞嘅方向發展 好撚唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd866fbabd8ac641a531757d68649100163726f","tid":1030104,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c6128567eabe6a2c74a2cacb8525ad2f08009243","tid":10301